TITLE: Implementing Application-wide Transaction Handling in FeathersJS
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to implement application-wide transaction handling in FeathersJS using Knex. It wraps create, update, patch, and delete operations in a transaction, handling both successful commits and rollbacks.
